Params:
LIGHT_TYPE (text): light type (Taxi, Strobe, ..) in proper case
ID (number, default: 1): light unique ID
[REQUIRED] VAR_NAME(bool): variable name
VAR_SCOPE(Text, default:L): Scope of the variable
-->
